{"tid":1976484,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Lilian Kan曬泳衣照被轟冇正面　24小時後終屈服派正面福利圖","createTime":"2020-04-17T09:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T12:42:26.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d59d73ed71a4def802366ea901679a4cb7284560","tid":1976484,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4339641/org/092ef218c7035ceb40f0ffbfcaa59719.jpg/R8Rgf6UGe-GR88JMc0yEFr9oB5f-IrPU4ucxZ-LnMWc?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4339641%2Forg%2F092ef218c7035ceb40f0ffbfcaa59719.jpg%2FR8Rgf6UGe-GR88JMc0yEFr9oB5f-IrPU4ucxZ-LnMWc%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=263ebb77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女神Lilian Kan（簡幗儀）IG擁有近22萬的追隨者。至於如何能俘虜這麼多粉絲，當然要擁有一副天使面孔，但憑這點也不能令她保持人氣高企。說實話比她漂亮的大有人在，會聽從粉絲意見，相信是讓粉絲這麼喜愛她原因之一是。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n在昨天（16日）她在IG發布一張泳衣照，可是這張照片只能觀看到她的背面，頓時粉絲們瘋狂要求她再發布多一照正面圖給大家觀看。經過一夜大家的要求，Lilian為了安慰暴動的他們，終於發布正面圖，她說：「說好的正面照，仲有側面，上年夏天在曼谷拍的。」短短一小時大批粉絲留言：「果然冇令我地失望。」"},{"pid":"3e42eaeadde3e9724b806cb973422775831c3ad4","tid":1976484,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:26:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4339509/org/438b03afb1d69562ae20aa2d8f9d35c6.jpg/YQu4APvwpAjAHaYyfi4Jfs6_q3yTug2CQCDgb0Ag4G8?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4339509%2Forg%2F438b03afb1d69562ae20aa2d8f9d35c6.jpg%2FYQu4APvwpAjAHaYyfi4Jfs6_q3yTug2CQCDgb0Ag4G8%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=00a7d2e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萬眾期望正面圖？（IG：liliankan ）"},{"pid":"11e5f5d53141017ea16b54e8f4b983f6ace86f85","tid":1976484,"uid":22839,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:27:05.000Z","msg":"30歲應該仲好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3277e8304f55549fd8